dc_title_s: Transports en commun de Bordeaux - Centre de la Ville de Bordeaux
dc_description_s: One map on front: Title = Centre de la Ville. Scale = 1:10,000. Street map of center of Bordeaux. Two maps on back: Transports en Commun de Bordeaux. Map on left: Title = Autobus - Reseau Suburbain. Scale = 1:90,000. Map of bus routes in greater Bordeaux. Map on right: Title = Autobus - Reseau Urbain. Scale = 1:32,000. Map of bus routes in Bordeaux city.
